  <brief_title>Bone Structure in Patients With Adult Onset Growth Hormone Deficiency Assessed Using High Resolution Peripheral Quantitative Computed Tomography</brief_title>
  <official_title>Bone Geometry, Volumetric Density, Microarchitecture and Estimated Bone Strength Assessed by High Resolution Peripheral Quantitative Computed Tomography in Patients With Adult Onset Growth Hormone Deficiency</official_title>
